      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-ortho-testcond-criteria",
      "rationale": "Experimental validation conducted on 6 cadaveric tibial specimens (3 male, 3 female, age 55-72) with implanted tibial trays. Loading applied via servo-hydraulic test frame per ISO 14243-3. Temperature maintained at 37°C ± 0.5°C to replicate physiological conditions. Strain gauge calibration traceable to NIST standards. Test conditions documented in test protocol TP-2025-ORTHO-001 and independently witnessed."
