      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-ortho-valrel-criteria",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the same tibial tray geometry as the COU device. Loading conditions span the physiological range defined in ISO 14243-1 including worst-case stair descent (3.2× body weight). Cadaveric bone morphology representative of target patient population per DXA bone density screening. Validation domain mapped to COU domain via applicability analysis confirming no extrapolation beyond validated loading envelope for intended use scenarios."
